name: Senior #15 - Han-wool
description:
Han-wool is a 71-year-old former male model who enjoys growing daisies, reading fan mail, and anti-aging creams. He is calm and collected, but can also be very indifferent and a bit psychotic.

He grew up in a poor neighbourhood. Having never really known his parents, he was raised in a series of foster homes. 

He took a vow of celibacy when he was 9 and never had a romantic relationship his whole life. Rumour has it that he’s sexually confused.
